Rating: 4
Very nice recipe. I too increased the Balsamic to 4 TBSP, and used the rind of a whole orange. I added 1 tsp of my own homemade vanilla extract (made with Jack Daniels and Vanilla beans). It compliments the date flavour and adds a nice background note. It's going to be a nice addition to our Thanksgiving dinner tomorrow. (Yes, in Canada our Thanksgiving is in October.)

